<plot>Lillian Porter wanted to love her husband; but Charles Kinsey, an abusive alcoholic, could never love her in return. Lillian returns to a life as a courtesan, wallowing in her guilt, when she learns that her husband has disappeared and that she is the only one who can find him. Her secret holds the key to finding Charles; but it is also a secret that will ruin both their lives forever- whether it is revealed or not.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?224468</url></doc>
